<h2><a name="begin" id="begin">begin</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Syntaxe:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;list&gt;</span>
    iterator begin<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span>;
    const_iterator begin<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span>;</pre>
<p>
A função begin() retorna um iterador apontando para o primeiro elemento da lista. begin() deve executar em <a href="http://www.cppreference.com/wiki/br-pt/complexity" class="wikilink2" title="br-pt:complexity" rel="nofollow">tempo constante</a>.
</p>

<p>
Por exemplo, o código a seguir usa begin() para inicializar um iterador que é usado para percorrer uma lista:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">     <span class="co1">// Cria uma lista de caracteres</span>
     list<span class="sy0">&lt;</span>char<span class="sy0">&gt;</span> lista;
     <span class="kw1">for</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">int</span> i <span class="sy0">=</span> <span class="nu19">0</span>; i <span class="sy0">&lt;</span> <span class="nu0">10</span>; i<span class="sy0">++</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="br0">&#123;</span>
       lista.<span class="me1">push_front</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> i <span class="sy0">+</span> <span class="st0">'a'</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span>;
     <span class="br0">&#125;</span>
&nbsp;
     <span class="co1">// Mostra a lista</span>
     list<span class="sy0">&lt;</span>char<span class="sy0">&gt;::</span><span class="me2">iterator</span> it;
     <span class="kw1">for</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> it <span class="sy0">=</span> lista.<span class="me1">begin</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span>; it <span class="sy0">!=</span> lista.<span class="me1">end</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span>; <span class="sy0">++</span>it <span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="br0">&#123;</span>
       <a href="http://www.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/009695399/functions/cout.html"><span class="kw3">cout</span></a> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="sy0">*</span>it;
     <span class="br0">&#125;</span></pre>
<p>

Tópicos relacionados: <a href="end" class="wikilink1" title="br-pt:stl:list:end">end</a>, <a href="rbegin" class="wikilink1" title="br-pt:stl:list:rbegin">rbegin</a>, <a href="rend" class="wikilink1" title="br-pt:stl:list:rend">rend</a>
</p>

